Compare with me, please, these two scriptures.

00:06:45.920 --> 00:06:54.319
The first one is in 1 Peter 5 in verse two.

00:06:54.319 --> 00:07:00.839
So speaking about the authority that Jehovah gives to shepherds, to elders, 1 Peter 5

00:07:00.839 --> 00:07:08.519
2 says, shepherd the flock of God under your care, serving as overseers.

