husband is the head of his wife.

00:07:43.970 --> 00:07:45.410
Well how does this apply then?

00:07:45.410 --> 00:07:48.209
How does this help our elder in our scenario?

00:07:48.209 --> 00:07:54.649
Well, his knowing the difference between the authority given here helps him to not overstep

00:07:54.649 --> 00:07:58.730
his authority as an overseer and as an elder.

00:07:58.730 --> 00:08:03.930
Of course, each situation is different, but depending on the situation, if this truly

00:08:03.930 --> 00:08:09.689
is a personal matter, he may very well modestly refrain from giving advice at all.

00:08:09.689 --> 00:08:15.129
He may not get involved at all, he may recognize this feels like husband territory and I'm

00:08:15.129 --> 00:08:19.889
going to allow her to work with her husband in this matter.

00:08:19.889 --> 00:08:24.089
And how does that benefit the couple?

00:08:24.089 --> 00:08:28.009
Well it preserves her husband's authority, doesn't it?

00:08:28.009 --> 00:08:32.090
It also deepens her respect for her husband as he is the one that can help to care for

00:08:32.090 --> 00:08:34.769
and help her in this situation.

00:08:34.769 --> 00:08:41.129
It keeps the strength of their marriage intact and their view of the sanctity of marriage.

00:08:41.129 --> 00:08:47.769
And it also avoids even an inkling of an emotional attachment forming between two people who

00:08:47.769 --> 00:08:51.750
are not married.

00:08:51.750 --> 00:08:58.190
Well these are just a few examples that highlight how our displaying modesty benefits others.

00:08:58.190 --> 00:09:04.750
And that is one of the most powerful motivations and reasons for displaying modesty.

00:09:04.750 --> 00:09:10.990
And sometimes considering how modesty benefits others gives us clarity of mind on what the

00:09:10.990 --> 00:09:17.470
modus course is and gives us the motivation to take that course.

