And as we considered, this is not just an alternate way of looking at it.

00:09:21.710 --> 00:09:27.070
This is not just a novel approach to showing modesty, but rather it is based on the second

00:09:27.070 --> 00:09:32.789
greatest commandment of the law, that is to love our neighbor as ourselves.

